      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain is complemented by a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-revving internals remain robust. The chassis retains its factory-tuned kinematics, offering exceptional steering feedback through the hydraulic rack. Finished in Interlagos Blue over Novillo leather, this example represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car with a firm pedal feel and linear power delivery across the entire rev range.",
